{
  "name": "RPlog_Making_New_Friends_Part_2",
  "title": "Making New Friends (Part 2)",
  "summary": "Led from Club Utinni to his storefront Gundark Industrial in Mos Eisley, the black-clad smuggler Tritus sounds out the free-trader Jaspar about hauling cargo with no questions asked. Testing him with a blaster and pointed scenarios about getting caught, Tritus is satisfied by Jaspar's professed willingness to move goods from A to B and stay ignorant of the details, and the two strike an accord. Their negotiation is interrupted by the swaggering, song-singing arrival of the Rattataki pirate captain Vane, who cheerfully throws her weight around. Tritus coolly makes clear he has no objection to dealing with pirates, trading veiled threats and laughter with Vane as he sizes up the new arrival. The scene ends with business agreed and an uneasy, colorful new partnership forming among smuggler, trader, and pirate.",
